The annual Women and Wine night was held at the Jacaranda Hotel on May 3. The event brings together women in business from different professions together for a night of engagement over a drink of wine.Presentations were made by the guest speaker human capital consultant Susan Wahugu and Women and Wine patron Terry-Ann Chebet of Keyara Organics.Others in attendance were Jacaranda Hotel's Liz Tapawa, Radio Africa Group senior account manager Amanda Ndirangu and Boutique Express CEO Caroline Muchina.